-- BigPoint to Hire 300 Employees This Year, Abendblatt Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-01-18T08:02:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-18/bigpoint-to-hire-300-employees-this-year-abendblatt-reports.html
Bigpoint GmbH, a Hamburg-based
online-games company, plans to hire 300 employees in countries
including  Germany , the U.K.,  France  and  Spain  this year, of
which 150 will be added in Hamburg,  Hamburger Abdendblatt 
reported today, without saying where it obtained the
information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  